## Architecture Overview

### State Filing Engine (LaunchFree + Distill Formation API)

Three-tier architecture for automated LLC formation submission:

- **Tier 1: State APIs** — Delaware ICIS PublicXMLService (confirmed), others TBD. Direct REST/SOAP integration.
- **Tier 2: Portal Automation** — Playwright headless browser automation for ~45 state portals. Per-state JSON config with form field mappings.
- **Tier 3: Print-and-Mail** — Automated via print-and-mail API service (e.g., Lob) for ~2-3 mail-only states.

Code lives in `packages/filing-engine/`, shared between `apis/launchfree/` (consumer, $0) and `apis/filefree/` B2B routes (Distill Formation API, $20-40/filing).

Payment orchestration: Stripe Issuing virtual cards for programmatic state fee payment.

### OCR Pipeline (Cloud Vision + GPT — Tiered)

```
W-2 Photo
    │
    ▼
[Pillow] → preprocess (auto-rotate EXIF, contrast, resize)
    │
    ▼
[GCP Cloud Vision DOCUMENT_TEXT_DETECTION] → hierarchical text + bounding boxes ($0.0015/page)
    │
    ▼
[Regex] → extract SSN locally, replace with XXX-XX-XXXX in all downstream text
    │
    ├─ [GPT-4o-mini structured output] → map scrubbed text to W-2 fields (~$0.001)
    │
    └─ low confidence (<85%) → [GPT-4o vision] → send actual image → extract fields (~$0.02)
    │
    └─ still low → Manual entry fallback
```

SSN extracted via regex locally. NEVER sent to any third-party API. Masked placeholder in all GPT contexts.
Google Cloud Vision does NOT store images, does NOT use them for training.

### Infrastructure (Zero AWS)

- Frontend: Vercel (Hobby tier, free — upgrade to Pro when needed) — filefree.ai, launchfree.ai, distill.tax, paperworklabs.com
- Backend: Render Starter ($7/mo, 512MB) x2 — FileFree API + LaunchFree API
- Portal Automation: Render worker (or dedicated) — Playwright workers for state portal automation
- Payment Orchestration: Stripe Issuing — virtual cards for state filing fees
- Database: Neon serverless PostgreSQL (free tier MVP)
- Sessions: Upstash serverless Redis (free tier: 500K commands/mo)
- Storage: GCP Cloud Storage (encrypted, 24hr auto-delete lifecycle)
- OCR API: GCP Cloud Vision (1K free pages/mo, then $0.0015/page)
- Local Dev: Docker Compose (`infra/compose.dev.yaml`) — DEV ONLY (postgres, redis, api, web)
- Production Deploy: render.yaml (Render Blueprints IaC) + Vercel git deploy
- Dev Tooling: Makefile (`make dev`, `make test`, `make lint`, `make format`, `make migrate`)
- Env Config: Single consolidated `infra/env.dev.example` for all services

